node.text:
Cheese Stuffed Chicken Parmesan Meatballs
INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley

Taco Mix:

Salt and pepper to taste
Chicken Fajita:
2 tsp oil
½ onion, diced
1 cup diced mixed peppers
2 tsp fajita seasoning
2 chicken breasts, cooked, shredded
2 tbsp tomato paste
2 tbsp water
Steak Fajita:
½ onion, sliced
1 cup sliced mixed peppers
2 rump steaks, thinly sliced
2 tsp fajita seasoning
2 tsp lime juice
Guacamole:
3 ripe avocados
1 small red onion, finely chopped
1 tbsp finely chopped coriander
½ tsp cumin powder
¼ tsp chilli powder
Juice of 2 limes
Salt and pepper to taste
8 large tortilla wraps
Sliced mozzarella
1 cups Grated cheddar cheese

Salsa
Sour Cream

node.text:
Up your sandwich game with this Italian Chicken Schnitzel Sando!

INGREDIENTS
Chicken
* 	2 chicken breast, butterflied and pounded thin
* 	2 lemons, juiced 
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 minced garlic cloves
* 	½ tsp Chilli flakes 
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	3 thyme sprigs 
* 	A few roughly torn sage leaves
* 	2 sprigs osemary
* 	Salt and pepper
* 	1 egg, beaten
* 	½ cup panko
* 	½ cup fine breadcrumbs
 
Slaw
* 	½ White cabbage 
* 	½ White onion, thinly sliced
* 	1 tbsp Honey 
* 	2 Lemons, juiced
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
 
Salsa verde
* 	30g Parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tbsp Capers, chopped
* 	½ red onion, finely chopped
* 	½ red chilli, finely chopped
* 	½ tsp Dijon
* 	3 tbsp Red wine vinegar 
* 	2 tbsp Olive oil 
* 	1 Anchovy
 
Artichoke Aioli
* 	1 egg yolk
* 	1 garlic clove
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
* 	Pinch salt
* 	2 artichoke hearts 
* 	1 lemon, juiced
* 	Vegetable oil - around 100ml
 
To serve
* 	Thick white bread

CROQUE MONSIEUR CROISSANT LASAGNA

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 shop-bought all-butter croissants
* 	a little butter for greasing
* 	1 1/2 cups bechamel sauce
* 	2 cups grated emmental cheese
* 	10 slices wafer thin cooked ham, plus a little more for layering
* 	nutmeg, a scrape
* 	dijon mustard, 1/2 tsp per croissant

node.text:
This recipe is a great arm hug in a pot! CRISPY CHICKEN WITH CREAMY BACON & MUSHROOM PASTA

INGREDIENTS
 3 chicken breasts
1 ½ cups plain flour
½ cup grated parmesan 
½ tsp garlic powder
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
2 tbsp chopped parsley
2 cups buttermilk
2 eggs, whisked
 
8 rashers bacon, chopped
1 tbsp butter
1 onion, diced
3 cloves garlic, minced
2 cups, sliced mushrooms
½ cup chicken stock
3 cups heavy cream
4 cups baby spinach
½ cup grated parmesan cheese
400g cooked linguine
Salt and pepper to taste

Cheese Stuffed Chicken Parmesan Meatballs
INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley

INGREDIENTS
Pizza Dough:
* 	¾ cup lukewarm water
* 	1 ½ packets yeast
* 	¾ cup water
* 	3 tbsp oil
* 	3 tbsp honey
* 	½ tsp salt
* 	4 ½ cups bread flour
Chicken Alfredo Mix: 
* 	2 tbsp butter
* 	3 cloves garlic, minced 
* 	2 cups heavy cream
* 	½ cup finely grated parmesan 
* 	3 chicken breasts, cooked and seasoned
* 	1 cup grated mozzarella
* 	1 cup ricotta 
* 	8 rashers bacon, cooked crispy and chopped 
* 	2 tbsp finely chopped parsley
 
Tomato Sauce: 
* 	2 tsp oil
* 	1 clove garlic, minced
* 	½ stp chili flakes
* 	2 cups passata
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
Pizza
* 	Sliced pepperoni
* 	Mozzarella
* 	Garlic butter

2 tsp oil
½ onion, diced
1 cup diced mixed peppers
2 tsp fajita seasoning
2 chicken breasts, cooked, shredded
2 tbsp tomato paste
2 tbsp water
Steak Fajita:
½ onion, sliced
1 cup sliced mixed peppers
2 rump steaks, thinly sliced
2 tsp fajita seasoning
2 tsp lime juice
Guacamole:
3 ripe avocados
1 small red onion, finely chopped
1 tbsp finely chopped coriander
½ tsp cumin powder
¼ tsp chilli powder
Juice of 2 limes
Salt and pepper to taste
8 large tortilla wraps
Sliced mozzarella
1 cups Grated cheddar cheese
1 cup grated mixed cheddar
Salsa
Sour Cream

node.text:
Up your sandwich game with this Italian Chicken Schnitzel Sando!

INGREDIENTS
Chicken
* 	2 chicken breast, butterflied and pounded thin
* 	2 lemons, juiced 
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 minced garlic cloves
* 	½ tsp Chilli flakes 
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	3 thyme sprigs 
* 	A few roughly torn sage leaves
* 	2 sprigs osemary
* 	Salt and pepper
* 	1 egg, beaten
* 	½ cup panko
* 	½ cup fine breadcrumbs
 
Slaw
* 	½ White cabbage 
* 	½ White onion, thinly sliced
* 	1 tbsp Honey 
* 	2 Lemons, juiced
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
 
Salsa verde
* 	30g Parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tbsp Capers, chopped
* 	½ red onion, finely chopped
